        "description": "Beam diameter for uniform cleaning; smaller for fine details (200-400 μm), larger for broad areas (500-1000 μm). 500 μm recommended for stoneware industrial apps to cover surfaces efficiently without hotspots. Source: Equipment specifications from Coherent and Trumpf laser systems for ceramic processing."
